import * as React from 'react'
import Head from 'next/head'
import {AppFrame, TitleBar, BottomNavigation, Navigation, MainContent} from 'material-ui-appframe'
import NavBar from './NavBar'

type Props = {
  title?: string
}

const Layout: React.FunctionComponent<Props> = ({
  children,
  title = 'XRChat',
}) => (

<AppFrame>
<Head>
      <title>{title}</title>
      <meta charSet="utf-8" />
      <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1.0, width=device-width" />
    </Head>
  <TitleBar>
  {title}
  </TitleBar>

  <Navigation>
<NavBar />
  </Navigation>

  <MainContent>
  {children}
  </MainContent>

  <BottomNavigation mobileOnly>
      {/* Bottom navigation for mobile devices. */}
  </BottomNavigation>
</AppFrame>
)

export default Layout
